apnay iman ki aabayari krain
dil ma Allah ka khof peda karain

subh-o-sham us ka azkaar ka wirad ho
or durood-e-nabi lab py jaari karain

meri millat ko mil jayn esay batal
jin k her ghaat pr ho nishaan-e-atal

ta k jab us k darbaar ma jayn hum 
dil ma kuch khof ho or na aakhain hon num

shok-e-jannat na manzil se pehlay ho kam
or sabeel-e-huda se hatain na qadam

